# compound-interest-lab
#
# This project is a fully static client-side application.
# It requires no environment variables, API keys, or secrets.
#
# All computation runs in the browser — there is no backend,
# no database, and no external service integrations.
#
# If you fork this project and extend it with a backend,
# document your required variables here following this pattern:
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
# VITE_SOME_PUBLIC_KEY=your_key_here
#
# Note: only variables prefixed with VITE_ are exposed to the
# browser bundle in a Vite project. Never put secrets in VITE_ vars.
